summary:
I

👏 am

👏 a

👏 lesbian

👏 and

👏 this

👏 is

👏 what

👏 I

👏 want

👏 All I can ever ask for is casual recognition. Allies...
body:
I 👏 am 👏 a 👏 lesbian 👏 and 👏 this 👏 is 👏 what 👏 I 👏 want 👏

All I can ever ask for is casual recognition. Allies changing icons, making harmless jokes, and hosting charity sales is the perfect thing to do to spread awareness and positivity while keeping everything relaxed and casual. Seeing some of my greatest role models supporting us just brightens my mood!

Let’s keep this month as positive as possible! Have fun at the parades, be who you are, and hold your head up high! Allies exist everywhere, and when we stand together, we’re so much stronger than if we were divided!
